headline: 5 Revealing Analyst Questions From Cencora’s Q4 Earnings Call
summary: Cencora's fourth quarter was marked by a negative market reaction, as revenue missed Wall Street’s expectations despite year-over-year growth. Management attributed performance to continued growth in its U.S. healthcare solutions, particularly specialty pharmaceuticals and new contributions from recent acquisitions.
